oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Patty and Harrell
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Dr. Robert Morris Patty (student in 1911) and Charlie Harrell (1961 ASB President) during the 50th Anniversary, from an issue of Sidelines

Dr. Robert Morris Patty of Covington, Georgia, discusses with Charlie Harrell, ASB president, the changes made since he was a student here in 1911-12. He was one of the first eight graduates of Middle Tennessee Normal in 1912.
